{{Top|leg}}
The '''Seinar Corporation''' was allied with [[Roganda Ismaren/Legends|Roganda Ismaren]] in [[12 ABY/Legends|12 ABY]]. Its president and many of its executive board were [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustans]].<ref name="Children of the Jedi novel">[[Children of the Jedi (novel)|''Children of the Jedi'']]</ref> [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] used a proton blaster manufactured by Seinar on [[Nam Chorios/Legends|Nam Chorios]] in [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]].<ref name="Planet of Twilight">''[[Planet of Twilight]]''</ref>

{{Company-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
"Seinar" may be a misspelling of "[[Sienar]]"; however, there is no known "Sienar Corporation," and all of Sienar's projects were not run by Sullustans. However, Seinar Corporation is mentioned several times throughout the novel, and it is always spelled the same way.

